          <h2 class="head-deatilpage">Privacy policy</h2>
          <p>This document defines the policies and practices that CheapAirHub uses to protect your personal information. Our goal is to protect personal information you provide us whenever you contact us or use this web site ("Site"). By visiting or using the Site, you are agreeing to these policies and practices.</p>
          <p>CheapAirHub may update this Privacy Policy in the future. You can tell when this Privacy Policy was last revised by referring to the "Last Updated" legend at the top of the page. Any changed to our Privacy Policy will become effective upon positing of the revised Privacy Policy.</p>
          <br />
          <h3 class="head-deatilpage">What information do we collect?</h3>
          <br />
          <h4 class="head-deatilpage">In General</h4>
          <p>We receive and store any information you enter on our Site or give us by telephone, e-mail, fax, or in any other way. This includes information that can identify you, including your first and last name, telephone number, postal and e-mail addresses, and, in some cases, billing information (such as credit card number, cardholder name, and expiration date), ("personal information"). We also may request information about your traveler preferences, including meal requests, seat selection, frequent flyer/hotel/car rental program information, and ticketing options. You can choose not to provide information to us, but in general some information about you is required in order for you to register as a member; purchase products or services; complete a traveler profile; participate in a survey, contest, or sweepstakes; ask us a question; or initiate other transactions.</p>
          <br />
          <h4 class="head-deatilpage">Passenger Information</h4>
          <p>When you make travel or other arrangements for someone else through CheapAirHub, we will request personal information and travel preferences about that individual. You should obtain the consent of other individuals prior to providing CheapAirHub with their personal information and travel preferences, as any access to view or change their information will be available only through your account.</p>
